post_content.caption: Trump team's First Amendment argument is 'so weak' in Georgia election interference case
post_content.description:
Former President's Trump's legal team is arguing at a hearing today to dismiss the Georgia election interference case. MSNBC legal correspondent Lisa Rubin, former Fulton County Deputy DA Melissa Redmon and former U.S. attorney Barbara McQuade weigh in.
